      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just being overwhelmed. it's that i see them looking at me when they think i'm not looking. that look of... pity. or just being tired of having to help me move or cook or whatever. if i weren't here, they'd finally have their lives back. they could travel, they could relax, they wouldn't be constantly worried about me. it almost feels like the most selfless thing i could do is just... step aside.",
